## IOperationExecutionResult.getStateHash() method

> This API is provided as an alpha preview for developers and may change based on feedback that we receive. Do not use this API in a production environment.
> 

Gets the hash of the state of all registered inputs to this operation. Calling this method will throw if Git is not available.

**Signature:**

```typescript
getStateHash(): string;
```
**Returns:**
